{"ts":"2026-06-27T04:42:08.735Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Exploring Design Components**\n\nI'm checking `app/portal/billing/page.tsx` for existing icon usage, and considering standard imports from `lucide-react`. I have Next 16.2.9, React 19.2.4, and Tailwind 4. This seems like a great start to begin designing the standard layout!\n\n\n**Defining Billing Page Structure**\n\nI'm now focusing on `/portal/billing/page.tsx`, and I've outlined the core content. I've broken it down into billing summary metrics, invoice lists with statuses, a contact card, and a suite of interactive elements. I am thinking about how to handle \"Validate Treasury Cert\" and \"Copy invoice reference hash\", along with a strong, responsive layout. I'm also examining the `previewInvoices` data and considering project associations like `GFF-2026-0899` to `GFF-2026-0988`.\n\n\n**Crafting Premium Billing Design**\n\nI'm now striving to avoid an AI-generated aesthetic. My goal is a high-fidelity billing page, matching enterprise standards and echoing the existing layout. I'm focusing on bespoke elements, including a cryptographic certificate header and a bento grid for high-fidelity metrics. I'm imagining interactive features, like a verifying flow, and a live recent invoice ledger, ensuring a modern, custom, and premium feel.\n\n\n**Refining Invoice Details**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the `/portal/billing/page.tsx` file, specifically the interactive invoice preview. I'm imagining interactive action buttons and associated project metadata. A key element is the Billing & Direct SWIFT Contact Card, providing highly professional wire transfer guidance. I'm also planning a custom side-drawer or modal for Invoice Details, triggered by invoice clicks. I will be checking similar dynamic page views to ensure design element consistency. Now, I am exploring a code-first approach. I will draft `app/portal/billing/page.tsx` and work with mock data. I am assessing `motion` but might favor Tailwind transitions.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T04:42:08.751Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"mw7410uf","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/portal/billing/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { \n  ArrowRight, \n  CreditCard, \n  ShieldCheck, \n  RefreshCw, \n  Download, \n  Copy, \n  Check, \n  User, \n  FileText, \n  ExternalLink,\n  ChevronRight,\n  TrendingUp,\n  Cpu,\n  Mail,\n  HelpCircle,\n  Clock,\n  Briefcase\n} from \"lucide-react\";\n\n// Project mapping for invoices\nconst INVOICE_PROJECTS: Record<string, { name: string; id: string; contact: string }> = {\n  \"GFF-2026-0899\": { name: \"Retail Mesh Core A1\", id: \"proj-retail-mesh\", contact: \"retail.ops@gff.ai\" },\n  \"GFF-2026-0914\": { name: \"Sovereign Mining Loop\", id: \"proj-oremesh\", contact: \"mining.ops@gff.ai\" },\n  \"GFF-2026-0945\": { name: \"Singapore Sandbox Enclave\", id: \"proj-singapore\", contact: \"sing.ops@gff.ai\" },\n  \"GFF-2026-0988\": { name: \"Multi-Agent Inference Cluster\", id: \"proj-multiagent\", contact: \"agent.ops@gff.ai\" },\n};\n\nexport default function ClientBillingPage() {\n  // Key state management for premium interactive elements\n  const [verifying, setVerifying] = useState(false);\n  const [verificationLogs, setVerificationLogs] = useState<string[]>([]);\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<\"summary\" | \"projects\">(\"summary\");\n  const [copiedInvoiceId, setCopiedInvoiceId] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  const [selectedInvoice, setSelectedInvoice] = useState<any | null>(null);\n  const [contactSuccess, setContactSuccess] = useState(false);\n  const [contactMessage, setContactMessage] = useState(\"\");\n\n  const previewInvoices = [\n    {\n      id: \"GFF-2026-0899\",\n      date: \"2026-06-01\",\n      amount: \"14,820.00 USD\",\n      status: \"paid\",\n      dueDate: \"2026-06-15\",\n      category: \"Compute Epoch\",\n      hash: \"0xDE897FF021BC8102C019FFAD998E1256E3B890CC7FFADE138EE87A02FF90A11B\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"GFF-2026-0914\",\n      date: \"2026-06-15\",\n      amount: \"3,500.00 USD\",\n      status: \"paid\",\n      dueDate: \"2026-06-30\",\n      category: \"SLA Support\",\n      hash: \"0x11B8A02FEE907C10BDE8267FEE10BC91A23D4FFA289F02ECBC12A349CDE150FA\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"GFF-2026-0945\",\n      date: \"2026-06-25\",\n      amount: \"24,900.00 USD\",\n      status: \"processing\",\n      dueDate: \"2026-07-10\",\n      category: \"Telemetry Stream\",\n      hash: \"0x8FDE3102C130D7B2D26788AB0E8A850CE3207FFCDE10B74E824A45B12A4F23AA\"\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"GFF-2026-0988\",\n      date: \"2026-06-27\",\n      amount: \"8,250.00 USD\",\n      status: \"unpaid\",\n      dueDate: \"2026-07-15\",\n      category: \"Compute Epoch\",\n      hash: \"0x3FBC128EE809FF9CC9810A88AA11B8FFFA02CE8274A08B0192A45C89FBC10492\"\n    }\n  ];\n\n  // Cryptographic Ledger Verification Simulation\n  const handleVerifyLedger = () => {\n    setVerifying(true);\n    setVerificationLogs([]);\n    const logSteps = [\n      \"Establishing dual-socket SSL handshakes with Treasury HSM...\",\n      \"Requesting cryptographic proof-of-work (Intel SGX Quote v4)...\",\n      \"Validating 4 registered secure enclave telemetry signatures...\",\n      \"Comparing ledger entries with SHA-256 root certificates...\",\n      \"SUCCESS: Sovereign GFF Ledger is 100% synchronized and sealed.\"\n    ];\n\n    logSteps.forEach((log, index) => {\n      setTimeout(() => {\n        setVerificationLogs(prev => [...prev, `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] ${log}`]);\n        if (index === logSteps.length - 1) {\n          setVerifying(false);\n        }\n      }, (index + 1) * 650);\n    });\n  };\n\n  // Copy to Clipboard Utility\n  const handleCopyHash = (text: string, id: string) => {\n    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);\n    setCopiedInvoiceId(id);\n    setTimeout(() => setCopiedInvoiceId(null), 2000);\n  };\n\n  // Finance Liaison submission handler\n  const handleContactSubmit = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    setContactSuccess(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setContactSuccess(false);\n      setContactMessage(\"\");\n    }, 5000);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-8 pb-12\">\n      {/* Premium Narrative Header */}\n      <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030303] p-6 md:p-8\">\n        <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none\" />\n        <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full filter blur-3xl pointer-events-none\" />\n        \n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6 relative z-10\">\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">\n                Treasury Node Connected\n              </span>\n              <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse\" />\n            </div>\n            <h1 className=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono uppercase\">\n              Sovereign Spend & Bill Ledger\n            </h1>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-white/50 mt-1 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed\">\n              Verify cryptographically sealed enterprise commitments, inspect real-time SLA compute quotas, and review verified epoch statements.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          \n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n            <Link\n              href=\"/portal/billing/invoices\"\n              className=\"inline-flex h-11 px-5 rounded-lg bg-white hover:bg-white/95 text-black font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider items-center gap-2 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-lg shadow-white/5\"\n            >\n              <span>Explore Invoices</span>\n              <ArrowRight className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Financial Bento Grid */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        {/* Card 1: Active Subscription Plan */}\n        <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-md p-6 space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <CreditCard className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Plan Parameters</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-green-400 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\">\n                Active\n              </span>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block font-mono uppercase\">Assigned Plan Level</span>\n                <span className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase mt-0.5 block\">Enterprise Infinite</span>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40 block\">BILLING PERIOD</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-semibold mt-0.5 block\">Monthly Enclave</span>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40 block\">SANDBOX CORES</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-semibold mt-0.5 block\">4 Cores Active</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Progress Indicator */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-2 pt-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[10px] font-mono\">\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40\">SLA COMPUTE CAPACITY USED</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">78.4%</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"h-1.5 w-full bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                  <div className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-[#00FFC2] rounded-full\" style={{ width: \"78.4%\" }} />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"pt-4 border-t border-white/5 mt-4 flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] font-mono\">\n            <span className=\"text-white/30\">Next invoice epoch:</span>\n            <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">July 15, 2026</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 2: Spending Ledger Core */}\n        <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-md p-6 space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <TrendingUp className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Consolidated Spend</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">YTD 2026</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block font-mono uppercase\">Total Certified Spent</span>\n                <span className=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white font-mono tracking-tight mt-0.5 block\">\n                  $51,470.00\n                  <span className=\"text-xs font-semibold text-white/40 ml-1.5 font-sans\">USD</span>\n                </span>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 font-mono text-[11px] border-t border-white/5 pt-4\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40 block\">SETTLED (PAID)</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-green-400 font-bold mt-0.5 block\">$18,320.00 USD</span>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40 block\">DUE / PROCESSING</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-amber-400 font-bold mt-0.5 block\">$33,150.00 USD</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"pt-4 border-t border-white/5 mt-4 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n            <Clock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" />\n            <span>Invoice <strong className=\"text-white font-normal\">GFF-2026-0988</strong> ($8,250) is due in 18 days.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 3: Interactive Security Verification */}\n        <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-md p-6 space-y-5 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <ShieldCheck className=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-400\" />\n                <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Cryptographic Security</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse\" />\n            </div>\n\n            <p className=\"text-[11.5px] text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-mono\">\n              Every ledger entry is certified and co-signed under zero-knowledge secure hardware. Tap below to verify our trust envelope connection.\n            </p>\n\n            {verificationLogs.length > 0 && (\n              <div className=\"rounded border border-white/5 bg-black p-3 font-mono text-[9.5px] text-white/80 space-y-1.5 max-h-[90px] overflow-y-auto select-text\">\n                {verificationLogs.map((log, idx) => (\n                  <div key={idx} className=\"leading-tight border-b border-white/[0.01] pb-1\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">&gt;</span> {log}\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          <button\n            onClick={handleVerifyLedger}\n            disabled={verifying}\n            className=\"w-full inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] text-[10.5px] font-mono font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:border-white/20 transition-all cursor-pointer disabled:opacity-50\"\n          >\n            {verifying ? (\n              <>\n                <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-spin text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                <span>COMMUNING WITH HSM SECURE SEAL...</span>\n              </>\n            ) : (\n              <>\n                <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-green-400\" />\n                <span>VERIFY LEDGER INTEGRITY</span>\n              </>\n            )}\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Invoice Ledger & Project Association Grid */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        {/* Main Left: Recent Invoices */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n            <div>\n              <h2 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Recent Certified Invoices</h2>\n              <p className=\"text-xs text-white/40 mt-0.5\">Epoch ledgers associated with active decentralized projects.</p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div className=\"flex bg-white/[0.03] p-1 rounded border border-white/5\">\n              <button \n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"summary\")}\n                className={`px-3 py-1 text-[10.5px] font-mono rounded uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer ${activeTab === \"summary\" ? \"bg-white/10 text-white font-bold\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n              >\n                Invoices\n              </button>\n              <button \n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"projects\")}\n                className={`px-3 py-1 text-[10.5px] font-mono rounded uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer ${activeTab === \"projects\" ? \"bg-white/10 text-white font-bold\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n              >\n                Projects Mapping\n              </button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {activeTab === \"summary\" ? (\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              {/* Desktop and Tablet Table Layout */}\n              <div className=\"hidden md:block overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table className=\"w-full text-left border-collapse font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 text-white/45 uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]\">\n                      <th className=\"pb-3 font-semibold\">Ledger ID</th>\n                      <th className=\"pb-3 font-semibold\">Category</th>\n                      <th className=\"pb-3 font-semibold\">Associated Project</th>\n                      <th className=\"pb-3 font-semibold\">Amount</th>\n                      <th className=\"pb-3 font-semibold text-center\">Status</th>\n                      <th className=\"pb-3 font-semibold text-right\">Actions</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-white/[0.02]\">\n                    {previewInvoices.map((inv) => {\n                      const proj = INVOICE_PROJECTS[inv.id] || { name: \"Central Sovereign Core\", id: \"central\" };\n                      return (\n                        <tr key={inv.id} className=\"hover:bg-white/[0.01] transition-all group\">\n                          <td className=\"py-3.5 pr-2 font-bold text-white group-hover:text-[#009DFF]\">\n                            {inv.id}\n                          </td>\n                          <td className=\"py-3.5 pr-2 text-white/60\">\n                            {inv.category}\n                          </td>\n                          <td className=\"py-3.5 pr-2 text-white/80\">\n                            <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1\">\n                              <Briefcase className=\"w-3 h-3 text-white/30\" />\n                              <span>{proj.name}</span>\n                            </span>\n                          </td>\n                          <td className=\"py-3.5 pr-2 font-semibold text-[#009DFF]\">\n                            {inv.amount}\n                          </td>\n                          <td className=\"py-3.5 pr-2 text-center\">\n                            <span className={`inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider ${\n                              inv.status === \"paid\" ? \"bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/25 text-green-400\" :\n                              inv.status === \"processing\" ? \"bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/25 text-[#009DFF]\" :\n                              inv.status === \"unpaid\" ? \"bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/25 text-amber-400\" :\n                              \"bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/25 text-red-400\"\n                            }`}>\n                              {inv.status}\n                            </span>\n                          </td>\n                          <td className=\"py-3.5 text-right space-x-1\">\n                            <button\n                              onClick={() => setSelectedInvoice(inv)}\n                              className=\"p-1 px-2.5 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 text-[10px] font-bold text-white transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                              title=\"Audit details and line items\"\n                            >\n                              Audit View\n                            </button>\n                            <button\n                              onClick={() => handleCopyHash(inv.hash, inv.id)}\n                              className=\"p-1 px-1.5 rounded border border-white/5 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-all inline-flex items-center justify-center align-middle cursor-pointer\"\n                              title=\"Copy SHA-256 seal hash\"\n                            >\n                              {copiedInvoiceId === inv.id ? (\n                                <Check className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                              ) : (\n                                <Copy className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                              )}\n                            </button>\n                          </td>\n                        </tr>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Mobile Responsive Layout */}\n              <div className=\"md:hidden space-y-4\">\n                {previewInvoices.map((inv) => {\n                  const proj = INVOICE_PROJECTS[inv.id] || { name: \"Central Sovereign Core\", id: \"central\" };\n                  return (\n                    <div \n                      key={inv.id}\n                      className=\"p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#030303]/40 space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px]\"\n                    >\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n                        <div>\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 block uppercase font-mono\">Ledger ID</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-white\">{inv.id}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <span className={`inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider ${\n                          inv.status === \"paid\" ? \"bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/25 text-green-400\" :\n                          inv.status === \"processing\" ? \"bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/25 text-[#009DFF]\" :\n                          inv.status === \"unpaid\" ? \"bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/25 text-amber-400\" :\n                          \"bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/25 text-red-400\"\n                        }`}>\n                          {inv.status}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 py-1\">\n                        <div>\n                          <span className=\"text-white/40 block text-[9.5px]\">CATEGORY</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-white font-medium\">{inv.category}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                          <span className=\"text-white/40 block text-[9.5px]\">DUE DATE</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-white font-medium\">{inv.dueDate}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"col-span-2\">\n                          <span className=\"text-white/40 block text-[9.5px]\">ASSOCIATED PROJECT</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-white font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 mt-0.5\">\n                            <Briefcase className=\"w-3 h-3 text-white/30\" />\n                            <span>{proj.name}</span>\n                          </span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"col-span-2 pt-1 border-t border-white/[0.03]\">\n                          <span className=\"text-white/40 block text-[9.5px]\">AMOUNT SETTLED</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold text-sm\">{inv.amount}</span>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 pt-2 border-t border-white/5\">\n                        <button\n                          onClick={() => setSelectedInvoice(inv)}\n                          className=\"h-8 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10px] font-bold text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                        >\n                          Audit Details\n                        </button>\n                        <button\n                          onClick={() => handleCopyHash(inv.hash, inv.id)}\n                          className=\"h-8 rounded border border-white/5 hover:border-white/25 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10px] font-bold text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                        >\n                          {copiedInvoiceId === inv.id ? (\n                            <>\n                              <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                              <span>Copied Hash</span>\n                            </>\n                          ) : (\n                            <>\n                              <Copy className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/50\" />\n                              <span>Copy Crypt Hash</span>\n                            </>\n                          )}\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <div className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                {Object.entries(INVOICE_PROJECTS).map(([invId, proj]) => (\n                  <div key={invId} className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:border-white/10 transition-all space-y-3\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start\">\n                      <div>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold block\">PROJECT ANCHOR</span>\n                        <h4 className=\"text-white font-bold text-sm mt-0.5\">{proj.name}</h4>\n                      </div>\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 uppercase bg-white/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">\n                        {proj.id.replace(\"proj-\", \"\")}\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1.5 text-white/60\">\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <span>Associated Invoice:</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{invId}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                        <span>Liaison Channel:</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2]\">{proj.contact}</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"pt-2 border-t border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center text-[10px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30\">Action Reference:</span>\n                      <button \n                        onClick={() => {\n                          setContactMessage(`Requesting clearance audit report regarding Project ${proj.name} tied to invoice ledger ${invId}.`);\n                          setSelectedInvoice(previewInvoices.find(i => i.id === invId));\n                        }}\n                        className=\"text-[#009DFF] hover:underline cursor-pointer\"\n                      >\n                        Request Audit Data\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Right Sidebar: Direct Treasury Contact */}\n        <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Treasury Liaison</h3>\n              <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40 font-mono mt-0.5\">Secure, non-automated communication channel.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                <div className=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#009DFF] font-bold text-xs\">\n                  TB\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-bold block\">Treasury Desk Berlin</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-[#00FFC2] block\">Verified GFF Agent</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-2 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 text-white/60\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>SWIFT Router:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-semibold\">GFF-AI-TREAS-BER</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Contact Point:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white\">treasury@gff.ai</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Sovereign ID:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-mono\">0xTRUST-BER-88</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <form onSubmit={handleContactSubmit} className=\"space-y-3 pt-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 block font-mono uppercase\">Direct Escalation Wire</span>\n              <textarea\n                value={contactMessage}\n                onChange={(e) => setContactMessage(e.target.value)}\n                placeholder=\"Inquire about custom rates, specific wire transactions, or core quota limits...\"\n                className=\"w-full h-24 p-3 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black text-[11px] font-mono text-white placeholder:text-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 resize-none\"\n                required\n              />\n              <button\n                type=\"submit\"\n                className=\"w-full h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded bg-white hover:bg-white/90 text-black font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n              >\n                Send Encrypted Inquiry\n              </button>\n            </form>\n\n            {contactSuccess && (\n              <div className=\"p-3 rounded-lg border border-green-500/20 bg-green-500/5 text-green-400 font-mono text-[10px] text-center\">\n                Secure handshake success. GFF Desk notified of inquiry.\n              </div>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"pt-4 border-t border-white/5 text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/35 leading-relaxed\">\n            Note: Bank-to-bank corporate wire transfers must specify the invoice hash references to ensure automated ledger validation at our SGX enclave nodes.\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Dynamic Drawer / Invoice Preview Overlay */}\n      {selectedInvoice && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 flex justify-end transition-all animate-[fadeIn_0.2s_ease-out]\">\n          <div className=\"w-full max-w-lg h-full bg-[#030303] border-l border-white/10 p-6 md:p-8 overflow-y-auto space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n            \n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              {/* Drawer Header */}\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\">\n                    Audit Transcript\n                  </span>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white font-mono mt-1.5\">{selectedInvoice.id}</h3>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/40 block font-mono mt-0.5\">Tied to {INVOICE_PROJECTS[selectedInvoice.id]?.name || \"Central Core Parameters\"}</span>\n                </div>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => setSelectedInvoice(null)}\n                  className=\"p-1.5 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer\"\n                >\n                  ✕\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Cryptographic Seal Hash */}\n              <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505] space-y-2 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-white/45\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-green-400 flex items-center gap-1\">\n                    <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                    <span>Cryptographic Seal</span>\n                  </span>\n                  <button \n                    onClick={() => handleCopyHash(selectedInvoice.hash, selectedInvoice.id)}\n                    className=\"text-[#009DFF] hover:underline flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer\"\n                  >\n                    {copiedInvoiceId === selectedInvoice.id ? \"COPIED\" : \"COPY HASH\"}\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/80 break-all select-all font-mono leading-relaxed bg-black p-2.5 rounded border border-white/[0.03]\">\n                  {selectedInvoice.hash}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Line Items Breakdown */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">Resource Cost Allocation</h4>\n                \n                <div className=\"space-y-2.5 divide-y divide-white/[0.02]\">\n                  {selectedInvoice.category === \"Compute Epoch\" && (\n                    <>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-1\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">Singapore Sandbox Zone-1 (Intel SGX)</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$6,500.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-2.5\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">Berlin Sandbox Zone-4 (AMD SEV)</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$4,800.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-2.5\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">eBPF Telemetry Hook Hooks (8 cores)</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$3,520.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </>\n                  )}\n\n                  {selectedInvoice.category === \"SLA Support\" && (\n                    <>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-1\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">Premium 24/7 Enclave Support Desk</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$2,000.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-2.5\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">HSM Secret Rotation Audit Provisioning</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$1,500.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </>\n                  )}\n\n                  {selectedInvoice.category === \"Telemetry Stream\" && (\n                    <>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-1\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">High-Fidelity eBPF Log Stream Pipeline</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$15,400.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-2.5\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">Decoupled Zero-Knowledge Data Relays</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$9,500.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </>\n                  )}\n\n                  {selectedInvoice.category === \"Premium Support\" && (\n                    <>\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-1\">\n                        <span className=\"text-white/60\">Direct On-Premise Sovereign Engineering Desk</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">$8,250.00</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </>\n                  )}\n\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between font-bold text-white text-[13px] pt-4 border-t border-white/5\">\n                    <span>TOTAL LEDGER AMOUNT:</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">{selectedInvoice.amount}</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Transaction Metadata */}\n              <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] space-y-2.5 font-mono text-[11px] text-white/50\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Timestamp Block:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white\">{selectedInvoice.date}</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Invoice Due Date:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white\">{selectedInvoice.dueDate}</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Standing:</span>\n                  <span className={selectedInvoice.status === \"paid\" ? \"text-green-400\" : \"text-amber-400\"}>\n                    {selectedInvoice.status === \"paid\" ? \"Settled Epoch\" : \"Awaiting Settlement\"}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-3 pt-6 border-t border-white/5\">\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => {\n                    alert(\"This simulates downloading a certified PDF receipt. Since this is a preview, no real file will be exported.\");\n                  }}\n                  className=\"h-10 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] text-[11px] font-mono font-bold text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                >\n                  <Download className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                  <span>Download PDF</span>\n                </button>\n                <button\n                  onClick={() => {\n                    setContactMessage(`Requesting settlement validation update regarding Ledger ${selectedInvoice.id} (${selectedInvoice.category}) for ${selectedInvoice.amount}.`);\n                    setSelectedInvoice(null);\n                  }}\n                  className=\"h-10 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-[11px] font-mono font-bold text-white flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/10\"\n                >\n                  <Mail className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                  <span>Inquire Desk</span>\n                </button>\n              </div>\n              <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 text-center font-mono\">\n                Sovereign financial signatures are compiled in real-time under HSM enclaves and registered to transaction logs.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
