ure the user experience is intuitive.\n\n\n**Adding Secure Wire Details**\n\nI'm now incorporating secure wire details. Specifically, I am adding encrypted non-automated wire support, and integrating a SWIFT router code and secure email channel for the treasury. I've also incorporated feedback functionality to register an inquiry for GFF desk notification. The goal is to provide a comprehensive and secure wire process.\n\n\n**Refining User Interactions**\n\nI'm now integrating a contact button for the GFF Treasury Desk into the UI. I'm focusing on its styling and functionality, aiming for a prominent and intuitive placement. I am incorporating a reminder about SWIFT metadata to enable instant enclave matching. I am now working on the invoice detail slide-out drawer, as the next stage in the workflow.\n\n\n**Finalizing Ledger Presentation**\n\nI'm now putting the finishing touches on the invoice display! I'm creating a clear and interactive preview, which includes the invoice ID, project details, and a close button. I'm also adding a crypto seal and copy ledger hash function. I've designed the visual elements for an intuitive and comprehensive invoice viewing experience. The goal is to make all details readily accessible. I will work on other components to improve the experience.\n\n\n**Displaying Invoice Data**\n\nI'm now integrating detailed invoice information within the slide-out drawer. Specifically, I'm displaying the hash, resource allocation details (category and amount), and invoice timestamp. I'm focusing on ensuring clear and concise presentation within the limited space. I'm aiming for easy readability.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T04:45:06.455Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"24rnpl6i","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/portal/billing/page.tsx","old_text":"        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}","new_text":"        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Invoice Ledger Section */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4\">\n          <div>\n            <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase\">Recent Certified Invoices</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/40 mt-0.5 font-mono\">Verified statements and corresponding localized project mappings.</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n            {invoices.map((inv) => (\n              <div key={inv.id} className=\"p-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#020202]/50 hover:border-white/10 transition-all space-y-3 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-white\">{inv.id}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30\">|</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/50\">{inv.category}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <span className={`inline-block px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[9px] font-bold uppercase ${\n                    inv.status === \"paid\" ? \"bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 text-green-400\" :\n                    inv.status === \"processing\" ? \"bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-[#009DFF]\" :\n                    \"bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 text-amber-400\"\n                  }`}>\n                    {inv.status}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-white/60 text-[10.5px] border-t border-b border-white/[0.03] py-2\">\n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9px]\">PROJECT ANCHOR</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{PROJECTS[inv.id]}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9px]\">DUE DATE</span>\n                    <span>{inv.dueDate}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9px]\">AMOUNT PREVIEW</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">{inv.amount}</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center pt-1 text-[10px]\">\n                  <button \n                    onClick={() => setSelInvoice(inv)}\n                    className=\"text-white hover:text-[#009DFF] hover:underline font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer animate-[fadeIn_0.15s_ease-out]\"\n                  >\n                    View invoice preview &gt;\n                  </button>\n                  <button \n                    onClick={() => handleCopy(inv.hash, inv.id)}\n                    className=\"text-white/40 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\"\n                  >\n                    {copiedId === inv.id ? \"COPIED REF\" : \"Copy ledger hash\"}\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Contact Treasury Card */}\n        <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Treasury Liaison Desk</h3>\n              <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono mt-0.5\">Encrypted non-automated wire support.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"p-4 rounded border border-white/5 bg-black space-y-2 font-mono text-[10.5px]\">\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9px]\">SWIFT ROUTER CODE</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">GFF-AI-TREAS-BER</span>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9px]\">SECURE EMAIL CHANNEL</span>\n                <span className=\"text-white font-mono\">treasury@gff.ai</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {inquirySent ? (\n              <div className=\"p-2 text-center rounded border border-green-500/20 bg-green-500/5 text-green-400 font-mono text-[10.5px]\">\n                Inquiry registered. GFF desk notified.\n              </div>\n            ) : (\n              <button \n                onClick={() => {\n                  setInquirySent(true);\n                  setTimeout(() => setInquirySent(false), 3000);\n                }}\n                className=\"w-full h-8 bg-white hover:bg-white/90 text-black text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase rounded transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n              >\n                Contact GFF Treasury Desk\n              </button>\n            )}\n          </div>\n          <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30 leading-relaxed font-mono\">\n            Always specify invoice ledger references in SWIFT metadata to enable instant enclave matching.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Invoice Detail Slide-out Drawer overlay */}\n      {selInvoice && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 flex justify-end\">\n          <div className=\"w-full max-w-md h-full bg-[#050505] border-l border-white/10 p-6 overflow-y-auto space-y-6 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-[#009DFF] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-mono font-bold uppercase\">Statement preview</span>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white font-mono mt-1\">{selInvoice.id}</h3>\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono block mt-0.5\">Project: {PROJECTS[selInvoice.id]}</span>\n                </div>\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setSelInvoice(null)}\n                  className=\"p-1 text-white/40 hover:text-white cursor-pointer text-sm font-mono\"\n                >\n                  [CLOSE]\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded bg-black border border-white/5 space-y-2\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between text-white/40 text-[10px]\">\n                    <span>LEDGER CRYPTO SEAL</span>\n                    <button onClick={() => handleCopy(selInvoice.hash, \"sel\")} className=\"text-[#009DFF] hover:underline animate-[pulse_1s_infinite]\">COPY</button>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/80 break-all select-all leading-relaxed bg-white/[0.02] p-2 rounded\">\n                    {selInvoice.hash}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[10.5px] font-bold text-white uppercase border-b border-white/5 pb-1\">Resource Cost Allocation</h4>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1.5 text-white/70\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                      <span>{selInvoice.category} SLA Allocation</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{selInvoice.amount}</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-white/[0.03] bg-white/[0.01] space-y-2 text-[10.5px] text-white/50\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                    <span>Invoice Timestamp:</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white\">{selInvoice.date}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                    <span>Epoch Due Date:</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white\">{selInvoice.dueDate}</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-3 pt-6 border-t border-white/5\">\n              <button \n                onClick={() => alert(\"Simulated PDF export initiated for ledger ID: \" + selInvoice.id)}\n                className=\"w-full h-9 rounded bg-white hover:bg-white/95 text-black font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n              >\n                <Download className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                <span>Download Certified PDF receipt</span>\n              </button>\n              <button \n                onClick={() => {\n                  setInquirySent(true);\n                  setSelInvoice(null);\n                  setTimeout(() => setInquirySent(false), 3000);\n                }}\n                className=\"w-full h-9 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] text-white font-semibold text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n              >\n                Contact Finance Desk\n              </button>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
